com.ae2dms.model.gameObject.sprite.projectile.BossProjectile
public class BossProjectile extends Projectile
Boss projectile The EnemyProjectile class handles the specificities with the projectile being shot from an enemy. For example, the enemy's projectile has a different color than the projectile of a hero. It also can only hurt a hero.
